  m_Name: NeighborJournal_16
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::JournalData
  id: 33
  title: "Nh\u1EADt k\xFD h\xE0ng x\xF3m #16 \u2014 B\u1EA3o v\u1EC7 chung c\u01B0"
  category: 3
  content: "T\xF4i l\xE0m b\u1EA3o v\u1EC7 t\xF2a nh\xE0 n\xE0y 12 n\u0103m. \u0110\xEAm
    qua l\xE0 \u0111\xEAm kinh ho\xE0ng nh\u1EA5t. Kho\u1EA3ng 10 gi\u1EDD, c\xF3
    ng\u01B0\u1EDDi g\xF5 c\u1EEDa \u1EA7m \u1EA7m. T\xF4i m\u1EDF th\xEC th\u1EA5y
    m\u1ED9t ng\u01B0\u1EDDi to\xE0n th\xE2n m\xE1u, m\u1EAFt tr\u1EAFng d\xE3. N\xF3
    lao v\xE0o c\u1EAFn t\xF4i. T\xF4i \u0111\u1EA9y \u0111\u01B0\u1EE3c v\xE0 ch\u1EA1y
    l\xEAn l\u1EA7u. B\xE2y gi\u1EDD t\xF4i \u0111ang \u1EDF ph\xF2ng b\u1EA3o v\u1EC7
    t\u1EA7ng 1, c\u1EEDa \u0111\xE3 kh\xF3a. Camera v\u1EABn ho\u1EA1t \u0111\u1ED9ng.
    T\xF4i th\u1EA5y ch\xFAng \u0111i theo c\u1EA7u thang l\xEAn t\u1EEBng t\u1EA7ng.
    Kh\xF4ng ai an to\xE0n n\u1EEFa."
  image: {fileID: 0}
  voiceLog: {fileID: 0}
